			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000976_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="3" unit="chars"/><placeName> 57 Sloane St</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="5" unit="chars"/>24<hi rend="sup">th</hi> March </p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear <persName>M<hi rend="sup">r</hi> Murray</persName></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>Many thanks 
<lb/>for the money &amp; 
<lb/>invitation. </p>
<lb/><p>I fear I cannot 
<lb/>come to dinner 
<lb/>but I shall see 
<lb/>when <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> L.</persName>
<lb/>comes in. I have 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_000976_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>another engagement 
<lb/>which she may 
<lb/>have got rid of 
<lb/>for me. I shall 
<lb/>let you know 
<lb/>before the evening<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>Believe me &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_000976_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'-->
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">I send XVIII-XXII 
<lb/>you have not 
<lb/>forgot the others 
<lb/>have you? </p>
			
